text = "[b]Goal[/b]
Tap falling coins and gems before they hit the danger zone at the bottom. Missing a good drop (or letting it cross the line) costs a life. You start with 5 lives — game over at 0.

[b]Scoring[/b]
• Gold coin: +1 (before combo)
• Silver: +5
• Diamond: +10
• Combo: every 5 good collects in a row steps the multiplier (×2, ×3, …)
• Small level bonus is added per tap on higher levels

[b]Levels[/b]
Every [b]150 score[/b] finishes the level you’re on (150 to reach level 2, 300 for level 3, then 450, …) — the game pauses, you tap the [b]Level N[/b] button, then the next level starts with faster drops (your total score keeps going). From level 4 onward, [b]bombs[/b] appear: tapping a bomb costs a life. From level 6, an extra speed tier kicks in. From level 9, twice as many items can be active at once.

[b]Tips[/b]
Your [b]score and level are saved[/b] automatically. After [b]Level Failed[/b], you have [b]5 retries[/b] total; each [b]Retry[/b] uses one. When all are used, wait [b]3 hours[/b] for them to refill before you can Play or Retry again. Boosters: ⚡ slower drops for a bit (uses one charge), ⏳ extra life that run (uses one charge). Counts are saved. Use Pause (||) for settings or main menu."

